headline.main: Fed Vice Chair Joins Effort to Flag Pending Rate Hike
headline.print_headline: Fed Vice Chair Joins Effort to Flag Pending Rate Hike

lead_paragraph: Federal Reserve policymakers who have recently signaled a pending U.S. interest rate rise are correct given the growing confidence and aggregate demand in the economy and stock market since the U.S. election, the Fed's vice chairman said on Friday.
